    <S id="S_0">
        <FORM>mlawa quyux nii na asi ka ml a seediq tnalang uciicin ka musa smkagun kesaun plawa quyux nii.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 有關求雨的這個儀式呢，一定要其他的部落的人去請求祈雨祭司。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> As for the ritual to pray for rain, it is neccesary to ask people in other tribes to request the shaman who prays for rain.</TRANSL>
